defaultThe role of the LTB will change in the context of the Strategic Economic Plan and the wider investment decisions that Comb
defaultined Authorities will make. SCR partners have always seen the LTB as part of a wider function of the CA and we are not surprised that the governance we are seeking to establish, matches Government
